  "translations": {
    "en": {
      "description": {
        "text": "Easily accessible bouldering area just under a kilometre from the centre of Sundbyberg. Part of a hill was blasted away to make room for two tennis courts, and the remaining rock has created an excellent bouldering area. Only a few problems have been established so far, with plenty of potential for more. Best in the afternoon when it gets the sun. Section C is wet in spring.",
        "method": "llm",
        "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
        "sourceIds": [
          "legacy:lotsjobouldern"
        ]
      },
      "sections": {
        "allmant": {
          "title": {
            "text": "General",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:lotsjobouldern"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "An easily accessible bouldering area just under a kilometre from central Sundbyberg. Parts of a hill were blasted away to make room for two tennis courts. What remains of the hill has created an excellent bouldering area. Only a few problems have been established so far, and there is excellent potential for developing more. Better in the afternoon when it catches the sun. Sector C is wet in spring.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:lotsjobouldern"
            ]
          }
        },
        "vagbeskrivning": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Directions",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:lotsjobouldern"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "Easy to reach by metro. Get off at Duvbo. Follow Tulegatan eastwards. Turn up Rensgatan. You will arrive directly at a car park. Cross the car park and head up towards the tennis courts. The crag is to the right of the courts.\n\nBy bus 515, get off at Sundbybergs Idrottsplats. The crag is about 50 metres away.\n\nIf arriving by car, there is plenty of parking along Tulegatan.\n\n=Sketch=\n\nNOTE – I suggest downgrading some problems that feel easier than their grade; see the discussion page. // Sasq",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:lotsjobouldern"
            ]
          }
        },
